# DevOps Requirements 

* Good understanding of Operating System (Linux, Microsoft, Apple IOS, Google)

* Understanding of network protocols 

* Understanding of version control tool (Git)

* Understanding of Configurtation Management (Puppet, Chef, SALTSTACK , Ansible, SolarWinds, CFEngine)

* Understanding of container technologies (Docker, Kubernetes)

* Infrastructure Knowledge AWS/ VMWARE

* Knowledge of Coding (Python/ Java/ CSharp)

* Knowledge of shell scripting (Powershell/ Javascript)

* Knowledge of different types of databases and different sql commands

